    She was shot in the stomach by Jake. He says "It took two shots but I did it" and then when he holds up his hand, it's blooding from her stomach. She <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    She was shot in the stomach by Jake. He says "It took two shots but I did it" and then when he holds up his hand, it's blooding from her stomach. She physically died. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
