        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer71892653" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9607980780094360255">LIVING DEAD GIRL is amazing, heartbreaking, and beautiful. I was terrified and intrigued. I had to carve a dark place in my heart to store this book, and I will be haunted for weeks.</span>

          </span>
